      <div class="hero-unit">
        <p><h2><a href="/blog/blog/gitWatcher-is-built-on-top-of-several-amazing-ruby-gems.html">GitWatcher is built on top of several amazing Ruby Gems</a></h2>24 Mar 2012 - 左左</p>
        <p>I&#39;d like to thanks one by one all the developers who contributed directly or undirectly to the amazing edge we are living in Ruby domain. Here it is a dump of Ruby Gems which GitWatcher is currently built on top of. My personal special thanks goes to MongoID project and in special way to durran...</p>
